Lois Sturt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lois_Sturt 0 The Hon. Lois Sturt (25 August 1900 – 18 September 1937) was one of the Bright Young Things of the 1920s. Later the lover of the Earl of Pembroke and the Duke of Kent, she married Evan Morgan, 2nd Viscount Tredegar.
